A sequel, titled Murder in the Making, was published by HarperCollins in 2012<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.harpercollins.com/9780062065438/agatha-christie-murder-in-the-making|title=Agatha Christie: Murder in the Making - John Curran - Paperback|publisher=}}</ref>.
