{{distinguish|Jean-Yves Lacoste}} '''Jean Lacoste''' (born 1950 in [[Paris]]) is a French-German philosopher, scholar and essayist. He is known for his research on [[Nietzsche]], [[Goethe]], [[Walter Benjamin]] and [[Ernst Cassirer]]. He is currently a philosophy professor at the [[Ecole Normale Supérieure]].<ref>[http://www.zahar.com.br/autor/jean-lacoste Jean Lacoste]</ref><ref>[http://www.lemonde.fr/livres/article/2012/12/07/jean-lacoste-romain-rolland-s-efforce-d-etre-le-plus-lucide-possible_1800587_3260.html Jean Lacoste, éditeur du "Journal de Vézelay"]</ref><ref>[http://www.franceculture.fr/oeuvre-l-aura-et-la-rupture-essais-sur-walter-benjamin-de-jean-lacoste.html L'aura et la rupture : essais sur Walter Benjamin Syndiquer le contenu]</ref>
